title: Denver Ghostbusters DVD SL 0.92 iso
description:
This DVD contains the entire Denver Ghostbusters saga:

Freddy Vs Ghostbusters (2004)
The Denver Chronicles (enhanced comic)
Return of the Ghostbusters (2007)

If you are not familiar these are non-profit, fan films by Braxtanfilm. Freddy Vs Ghostbusters is a short film the was quite a hit on the internet. Return of the Ghostbusters is quite a spectacular feature length film and a must see for any Ghostbusters fan. Both feature excellent writing and superb special effects.

This DVD iso is intended for Single Layer DVDRs and is formatted for 4:3 screens, letterboxed. It features English and Portuguese subtitles, a Score Only track on RotGB and a couple Easter eggs.
